Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.11,0:00:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,配备着以电脑为导航系统的赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“CYBER F0RMULA”正式登场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.39,0:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代替“F-l”的2l世纪赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.17,0:00:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令全世界人都狂热起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,!Effect,新世纪GPX “CYBER F0RMULA”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.08,0:00:33.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快快出发 不用有任何担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.56,0:00:40.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会帮助你 因为喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.98,0:00:43.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可思议的悸动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来自你求助的讯号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.73,0:00:53.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从昨夜开始一直感觉得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.62,0:01:00.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突如其来的风暴阻挡了前进的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.33,0:01:04.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愿望便浮现在眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是喜欢 是奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.51,0:01:15.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都会放在心上 不论什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的波浪会紧随而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.23,0:01:27.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在马上出发 决不动摇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.80,0:01:33.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了实现梦想 永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.15,0:01:43.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快快出发 不用有任何担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.75,0:01:50.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会帮助你 因为喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.68,0:01:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人所属的管生阿斯拉达队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正朝向巴西的新里约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.68,0:02:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备参加世界赛的第三战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.69,0:02:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个场地直线很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.82,0:02:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何在这个弯道超车\N是比赛的重点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.73,0:02:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了\N关键就在于如何运用煞车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干什么?伸介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是大楼风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.67,0:02:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,风势相当的强劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下子我看是有点棘手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不过是风大了点嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.68,0:02:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且阿斯拉达的尾翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.65,0:02:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是刚好可以藉着风的阻力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.98,0:02:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,增加它的贴地性吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 在接近极速的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.32,0:02:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,控制阻力太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.75,0:02:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕速度会没有办法加快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.69,0:02:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是如果改变尾翼的角度的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.99,0:02:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而可能会被风吹翻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车田叔他说这次比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.63,0:02:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要把车子改成高速用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.23,0:02:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介 你认为\N车田叔这个提议可行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.30,0:02:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是典型的高速场地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然这么做很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想一定有很好的效果的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.96,0:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十七话  友情演唱会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.66,0:03:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长 你看起来蛮高兴的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是等一下有约会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.70,0:03:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 怎么会有人跟我约会嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.23,0:03:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且就算有的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.03,0:03:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事对我来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可比约会还重要呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.61,0:03:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.81,0:03:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪 风怎么这么强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.98,0:03:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把路面检查过后马上就回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.18,0:03:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到了没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.69,0:03:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要把阿斯拉达改装成高速用车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,风阻零件还有高速的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概中午左右就会到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家要准备一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.83,0:04:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说上午就要开始工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.84,0:04:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距离预赛只剩下三天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要在预赛之前完工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一次无论如何一定要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.11,0:04:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让隼人上颁奖台去领奖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.24,0:04:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车田叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天再开始可不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么啦 你是不是有事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.32,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,零件到了以后就开始好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良平 你也是一样喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.33,0:04:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.73,0:04:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一次就看我们的好了 对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.77,0:04:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看 还是跟车田叔说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尾翼没有调整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三战的场地尾翼的角度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是影响胜败的关键
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.09,0:04:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你身为职业的维修员\N应该知道这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新条先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的失误就是我的过失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请原谅他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.90,0:05:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又不是希望你们来道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.84,0:05:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是希望你们做事情\N要像一个职业维修员而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家回去工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要上了一次颁奖台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以后就不想下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是所谓的赛车手嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是希望如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.03,0:05:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了达到这个目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我们不需要工作能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,达不到要求的工作人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的事情就交给我来办吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶 如果没有我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会得到第三名吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么好神气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.22,0:06:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我没有认错的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不就是\N阿斯拉达队的维修队长吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.23,0:06:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想请问你想不想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到我这里工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像阿斯拉达这种弱的队伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还能够拿到第五名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.24,0:06:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可见你的技术是相当的不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.41,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且像那种犯错的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你倒挺不客气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.75,0:06:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然了 我这样做不对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.69,0:06:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,维修员虽然有很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我对你的评价特别的高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.93,0:06:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你肯的话\N随时都欢迎你过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.49,0:07:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长 零件都到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.26,0:07:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟敢说我们是弱队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.69,0:07:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.33,0:07:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是什么人都会有自尊心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.03,0:07:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 开始工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 其他的工作就交给我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.21,0:07:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介把场地资料输进电脑里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.52,0:07:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车田叔 有点事想跟你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.38,0:08:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,演唱会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.81,0:08:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日期就是今天嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,格利合唱团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美树是他们的忠实歌迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介 你对摇滚乐很熟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.96,0:08:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种热闹的音乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的没有兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过这个合唱团的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.46,0:08:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是听过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.76,0:08:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新里欧足球场今晚七点钟开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难怪美树一副心不在焉的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.04,0:08:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美树这个丫头这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.31,0:08:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛不告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.44,0:08:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车田叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.11,0:08:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美树的责任感非常强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过听个演唱会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也花不了多少时间嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你是肯让她\N去听演唱会了是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自从出发以后都太紧张了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.32,0:08:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是美树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是有必要轻松一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.80,0:09:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到车田叔还有轻松的一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.30,0:09:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么叫没想到 真是太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像我 光是懂得电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他都一窍不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是车田叔的话\N我根本就不可能在这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.22,0:09:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要去听演唱会你就去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁说的都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易才买到的票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要浪费了 听到没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是良平这小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老实说我是很想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过现在不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.84,0:09:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必了?可是票都已经买好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.38,0:09:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车田叔肯让我去我心领了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.22,0:09:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我决定我不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.85,0:09:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.89,0:09:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是人没有不犯错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.62,0:10:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是把人当做机器一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.59,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个人到底是谁呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.06,0:10:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要在意演唱会的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到鼓舞了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.28,0:10:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对呀 一年前管生阿斯拉达队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招募新人的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.28,0:10:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是我跟美树刚进来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为是一个无名小卒的队伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.32,0:10:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以根本就没有人来应征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.09,0:10:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.99,0:10:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个时候美树她跟我说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.06,0:10:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就没有人来应微
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.60,0:10:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个队伍不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能持续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.97,0:10:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介 怎么办 你想留下来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.91,0:10:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道该怎么办才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.11,0:10:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.44,0:10:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除非老板说他要解敌这个队伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.91,0:10:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则的话我是不会走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.25,0:11:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的目标是要做一个\N世界级的维修员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以只要有队伍招人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就去应微
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不管到那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是说太年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.49,0:11:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是说女孩子不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.13,0:11:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我当时非常的沮丧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.23,0:11:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一个全部由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女孩子组成的\N摇滚合唱团格利吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.64,0:11:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个时候我听了她们的歌之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得我受到很大的鼓励
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个歌词我到现在都还没忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歌词是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道怎么搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觉得自己信心十足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.41,0:12:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要再试一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.35,0:12:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个合唱团就在这啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对呀 当时车田叔跟经理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.49,0:12:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只问我想不想做维修员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.42,0:12:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他的一律没有提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我就决定要留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到解敌为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.57,0:12:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这样所以才那么想去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就更该去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.41,0:12:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊 现在去还来得及嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.39,0:12:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你听好 良平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是维修员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.42,0:12:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是做好车子的维修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去听啊 队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.86,0:12:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就交给我来做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一边工作一边在想这个事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你是在葵车队的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你早就被开除了你知不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.41,0:13:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.38,0:13:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算赛车的成绩再不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不可以把责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.75,0:13:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,归罪于维修员的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.91,0:13:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想美树她一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.88,0:13:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很想去听演唱会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是她又不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.75,0:13:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们又有什么办法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 还有明白香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.93,0:13:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个帮我个忙好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介 我们的运气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的还蛮不错的\N居然买到票了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.71,0:13:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用电脑预约的刚好有五张退票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,运气不错可以完成美树心愿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真怕被美树知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们偷偷跑去帮她买票的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.82,0:13:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她们两个人一做起事情来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.96,0:14:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对周遭的事情完全都不顾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.13,0:14:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你放心好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.46,0:14:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介 开快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.96,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介 快点准备录音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 把这个戴上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.41,0:15:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.95,0:15:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电视台的臂章啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,演唱会是不准录音的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.02,0:15:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我就假装要采访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.92,0:15:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经跟主办单位联络过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.92,0:15:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是向电视台的人借的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不愧是伸介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 你负责右边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.26,0:15:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左侧呢由明日香来负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总算把引擎给弄好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.31,0:15:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了 队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个维修员他真的被解雇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.12,0:16:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解雇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.16,0:16:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是葵队的维修员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.18,0:16:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢 大家好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.39,0:16:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一首曲子是埋所当然的奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪 大家都跑到那里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.54,0:16:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不晓得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.54,0:17:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是道地的巴西咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.68,0:17:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车田叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事让我来做就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们装引擎也够累的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.52,0:17:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车子情况现在怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.29,0:17:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的明天一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以全部做完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.19,0:17:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那明天我也来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.16,0:17:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.63,0:17:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们去那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.00,0:17:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没去那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明日香 菜愈烧愈好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做的薯泥很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实那是隼人做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.08,0:17:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.08,0:17:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.49,0:17:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.53,0:17:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介在叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.39,0:17:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有很重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.46,0:17:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟他说我吃完饭\N马上就过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看啊还是拿到里面吃好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.10,0:18:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.34,0:18:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在搞什么鬼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别管了 快点来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遥控器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 请你慢慢的欣赏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什么事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.65,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你们就到了演唱会现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.22,0:18:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车田叔 你说他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去买东西的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.32,0:18:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不过是在\N遵照大家的指示行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望她会喜欢那个礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你放心好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她绝对不会失望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸介这小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.85,0:20:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到他还记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.53,0:21:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美树跟伸介刚刚来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.63,0:21:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是我跟我老板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要再度跟我们理想挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.93,0:21:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然大家都想要试试看\N那我们就试试啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我当时也是为了美树的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.87,0:21:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要留下那句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.87,0:21:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才留在这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.74,0:21:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个人都有他的过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.38,0:21:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才会有现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.61,0:21:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也会加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.35,0:21:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是为了将来能够\N跟大家一起创造美好的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.25,0:21:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.36,0:21:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良平 吃完饭开始工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.46,0:21:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美树 你慢慢欣赏嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.63,0:21:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然现在有录影带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我每天都可以看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他人目光没有在背后注视着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为肩负着使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相互信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下双手 仰望天空时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相互信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有现在加倍努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能有明天的辉煌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此 不用后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向着自己树立的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎着风前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最终我们会是胜利者

